{"tid":1471790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼既重要性?","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:21:55.000Z","uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01e5f899c4e4d894da3e12c9a965e4dc75c6b7ca","tid":1471790,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"1: 抽出愈多就夠證據比媒體及外國政府做野, 由其美國有關香港人權法, 禁佢及家屬美國資產入境權, 留資產起大灣區, 幫中共減資金外流~<br />\n2: 抽出後對佢愛護有家, 給予充滿愛的動作. 如果捉完就放, 無愛既回應, 佢地就會不斷上門, 因無成本可言, 所以只需一兩次深深的愛就有機會阻嚇到, 增加佢地心理壓力<br />\n3: 可能隻鬼就係傷害我地既人~或影低手足個樣<br />\n4: 助人助國, 呼籲佢地申請器官捐贈及參軍<br />\n5(壞處): 如處理不當, 有機會比媒體影到, 比外面有機會有負面印象~<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7462469cec09e42ecb5fab7fa036d7447385cf26","tid":1471790,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.c